item.title: A little bit about me.
item.description: “Anything that can go wrong will go wrong.” – Murphy’s law 1 A little something about me, I am but a humble student who was lost for so long but is finally found. :) It took me quite a while to end up with cybersecurity and I am more than happy that I did. As they say, some beautiful paths cant’t be discovered without getting lost.2 Besides being a full time student and going down this rabbit hole called “cybersecurity” totally of my own accord, I love to travel around whenever I can.
